|----------------------|--------------|------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Instrument            | N/A           | Name (string), Type (string)              | Play()                                                                   |
| StringInstrument      | Instrument   | Strings (int), Pitch (int), Tone (string) | PluckString(stringNum), ChangePitch(), ChangeTone()                       |
| WindInstrument        | Instrument   | Reed (string), Volume (int), Tone (int)   | Blow(), ControlVolume(), ControlTone()                                   |
