What is the R code to create a 3-step party planning process that involves a language puzzle, mathematical puzzle, and logic puzzle, as well as a social media challenge that must be completed before moving on to the next step? The steps must be completed in a specific order and only after the previous step has been successfully completed. How can I also automate the process using R code?
